Doing it as a square in the middle of the screen would require some extremely precise timing, and you would NOT be able to give it per-pixel accuracy horizontally - even if you got it to stay perfectly still, the edges would still be rather jagged.<br /><br />Also, my demo is "Co<strong>p</strong>per Bars", not "Co<strong>o</strong>per Bars".<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://forums.nesdev.com/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=7">Quietust</a> — Mon Jan 16, 2006 3:40 pm</p><hr />
